Drink Champs: THE HANGOVER - In this edition of The Hangover our special guest Jaz-O joins The Hangover Crew! This week we try to recap the conversation had on Drink Champs.

Check out as Hazardis Soundz, Mr. Lee, Boris aka BeatsNdaHood, Sunny D BET, along with Jaz-O as they share some of their favorite moments from this weeks episode!
